Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.72,0:01:49.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斩吧，波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.37,0:02:02.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森   波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.05,0:02:19.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个笨蛋，好不容易痊愈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.89,0:02:21.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却为了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.93,0:02:26.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了我… 喜欢时就讲喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢死时就死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.00,0:02:32.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是死亡就什么都完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.44,0:02:37.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情都… 完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.71,0:02:39.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.56,0:02:57.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支配的王锡   统一罗德岛的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.23,0:03:01.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是·
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.91,0:03:09.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.44,0:03:15.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会错，这是我要找的太守秘宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.65,0:03:17.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支配的王锡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.75,0:03:22.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个，只要拥有那个王锡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗德岛就是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.19,0:03:26.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔道大人不能完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.32,0:03:28.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个统一罗德岛的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.99,0:03:31.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是我实现的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.80,0:03:34.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.47,0:03:37.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.88,0:03:52.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能那魔龙煞星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它不是离开去找食物了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以亚喜拉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在最好等古娄达他们来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.79,0:04:03.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是·
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在古代流传下来的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为魔法的关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.41,0:04:23.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有人想要拿走支配的王锡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.35,0:04:26.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管多远它都可以随时出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡修殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见，欧布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.56,0:04:36.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是亚喜拉吗，我有点记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.43,0:04:44.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这五年间我却没忘记过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里决一死战吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次吧，现在要先打败煞星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会帮忙我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想侮辱我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.95,0:04:59.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别心急，你的心情我很了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.62,0:05:04.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我对煞星比对你还要怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.66,0:05:12.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是，但是我和你也有仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.06,0:05:14.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想请你帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.50,0:05:19.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我的仇在打败煞星之後再了断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听讲支配的王锡有能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.04,0:05:27.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以让任何可怕的东西都降服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.31,0:05:31.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你看谁的同伴先到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先拿到支配的王锡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才可以成为新的胜利者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.76,0:05:44.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣，但是我看过你的奸计
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在与贝尔道大人打斗的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.03,0:05:53.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记，但那时因为没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.77,0:05:57.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就成为拯救罗德岛的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.14,0:06:01.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破坏一级圣约的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉大人这到底是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.18,0:06:08.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是五年前在英雄战争中的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是谁发出的箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射中贝尔道大人的肩膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.13,0:06:28.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙利用那一瞬间的漏洞打赢了大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来是可以不挥剑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.71,0:06:36.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是手却不自主的挥出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要解决掉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.12,0:06:43.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争之神要责骂我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.59,0:06:49.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱着必死决心也要保住罗德岛的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.29,0:06:52.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…但是 ....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡修殿下   是帕母吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用去和他谈条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉的同伴我们已经解决了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.97,0:07:06.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古娄达他们输了!怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.35,0:07:13.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他杀了然後再去杀魔龙煞星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.75,0:07:17.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母，我欠他一个债一定要还
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.96,0:07:20.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为骑士  身为一国之王的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.03,0:07:26.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要打倒魔龙煞星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.83,0:07:30.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱安抚精灵之歌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.87,0:07:31.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.07,0:07:38.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.28,0:07:39.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂都，把水精灵叫出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮卡修殿下挡住龙的火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾里你也使用玛发的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.52,0:07:49.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去帮忙掩护卡修殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用讲我也会这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.92,0:07:56.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撒哈拉的力量 广扩草原的心胸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.03,0:08:02.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大地之母玛发，请保护他们安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.40,0:08:07.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水的精灵舞笛，请帮战士闯过难关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.21,0:08:16.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你杀死以慰那些亡灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.71,0:08:18.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.05,0:08:21.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.26,0:08:33.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个眼睛…我来引开它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你趁机跑过去  但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在没时间考虑了   走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.97,0:09:19.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战之神麻利，请治疗这勇士的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.65,0:09:30.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉大人，你还没有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.03,0:09:44.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  能看到这种场面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.04,0:09:46.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以作出很棒的诗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.07,0:09:53.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，在煞星攻击下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.91,0:09:55.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舞笛力量越来越弱，这样下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.08,0:09:59.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万能之王法利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请赐力量使剑能除魔龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.51,0:10:37.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大地的精灵，拜托请听我请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的… 人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.82,0:11:09.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.64,0:11:33.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了，把魔龙煞星打败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.26,0:11:55.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡修殿下  亚喜拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.57,0:12:04.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等等亚喜拉大人，你的伤...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.64,0:12:07.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由你发出决战开始的讯号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.48,0:12:09.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欧布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.68,0:12:16.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以战之神麻利的名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.39,0:12:17.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始履行战士的圣约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.57,0:12:33.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡修他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂都   帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.61,0:12:36.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题，陛下会赢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.47,0:12:38.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.08,0:12:41.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果陛下有什么意外，到那时 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.62,0:12:55.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一定要决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.73,0:12:58.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们二个都是真正的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.60,0:13:03.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拥有理想  为理想去奋斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.47,0:13:10.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了成为真正德勇者，实现理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.98,0:13:15.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你错了  我不是勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我是夫雷国国王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.25,0:13:22.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候是要不管牺牲去保护一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.09,0:13:26.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会不去管火焰中的莱登城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.36,0:13:31.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是王，所以我有义务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.36,0:13:36.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被王这个名字绑住，你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.30,0:13:42.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样就让你和煞星一样下场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.54,0:13:46.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.93,0:14:08.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.40,0:14:17.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我居然会输，不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.38,0:14:21.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能，不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.11,0:14:27.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再争斗了，可不可以别再争了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.25,0:14:31.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么，为什么打不赢这个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.39,0:14:39.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…  一定要完成贝尔道王的遗愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.91,0:14:54.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了   不管怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么   帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.69,0:15:07.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉你忘记圣约了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的话我一定不会输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.50,0:15:19.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要拥有这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.90,0:15:23.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要拥有这个，我就是 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.55,0:15:34.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗德岛的统一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.22,0:15:40.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你使出全部最後的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.22,0:15:43.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你就会赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.76,0:16:17.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗德岛的统一  贝尔道王的遗愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.30,0:16:24.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.73,0:16:25.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.64,0:16:31.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人并没有忘记圣约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.14,0:16:33.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就随他去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔道王的遗愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.79,0:16:49.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的… 梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.90,0:16:58.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…亚喜拉大人违反圣约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是那样好的战士  那么好的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.74,0:17:05.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我看错了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.68,0:17:08.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇者也是个人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.11,0:17:12.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被梦想束缚着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候身体也会不听使唤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.22,0:17:20.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是个违反圣约的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.43,0:17:24.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡修殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.30,0:17:28.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要重新想过所以我要去旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.00,0:17:32.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣的勇气  圣的勇者到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.94,0:17:37.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後去了解为什么要战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.38,0:17:41.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果了解之後请再来夫雷国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.45,0:17:45.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还需要你的帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.45,0:17:47.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.32,0:17:51.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我在想...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母  真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了  帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.16,0:18:02.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那年轻战士也许是圣勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打赢了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.51,0:18:16.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我们是打赢了但是 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.95,0:18:20.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么是赢家  什么是败者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我救不了波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.92,0:18:28.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连… 他的心也 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.59,0:18:31.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤心的事已经结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.67,0:18:38.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会像以前，过自己喜欢的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.87,0:18:42.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.34,0:18:45.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是波里森用牺牲换来的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.34,0:18:49.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 你讲得对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.15,0:18:58.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样做对吧，波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.13,0:19:09.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.47,0:19:12.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧，回到我们的城市去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.47,0:19:15.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家帮忙守住的罗德岛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.04,0:19:18.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在阿烈克拉岛南方有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.31,0:19:20.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字就叫罗德岛的岛屿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.61,0:19:25.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在激烈战争下的罗德岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.55,0:19:28.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在又有新的勇者的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.59,0:19:33.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇者的心里面将会牢记着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.69,0:19:36.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一个新的胜利者